  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA83">
<l>ayarppā yayarāppāy neñcamē coṉṉē</l>
<l>ṉuyappō neṟiyituvē kaṇṭāy ceyaṟpāla</l>
<l>vallavē ceykiṟuti neñcamē yañciṉēṉ</l>
<l>mallarnāḷ valviṉaṉai vāḻttu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Forget [or] don’t forget, heart. I said</l>
<l>this is the way we shall escape, see. [Things] that are not</l>
<l>to be done you may do, heart, I’m afraid,</l>
<l>praising the one with hard work on the wrestlers’ day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
